main event: On August 8, 1966, an observer reported sighting three unidentified objects in the sky over California, lasting approximately 15 minutes.
interesting points: The sighting was classified as a ground-visual observation., The observer stated they saw the objects moving in an unusual manner., No photos or physical evidence were provided., The sighting was recorded in the Project Blue Book series of reports., The observer was certain of the objects' movements and their presence.
witness description: The witness described himself as a 65-year-old male, providing limited detail about the sighting.
